    "These values are reflected in progressively greater accuracy in the DG and UDA settings compared to the \"Source Only\" settings (Table 2).",
    "Class alignment.",
    "For assessing the contribution of L c RNA, we show in Fig. 5 the evolution of the verb norms of the ten most frequent and the least frequent classes in the DG settings.",
    "In the \"Source Only\" (Fig. 5a) the per-class mean features norms are largely unbalanced.",
    "While the exclusive use of L g RNA contributes to a better global balance of the modality norms, it has a small effect on the balancing of the norms per-class (Fig. 5b)."
